name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent, v. Aaron JONES, Petitioner

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent, v. Aaron JONES, Petitioner.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM:
AND NOW, this 12th day of November, 1996, the Petition for Writ of Prohibition and King’s Bench Power is denied.
The Petition for an Emergency Stay of Execution is GRANTED until resolution of the currently pending PCRA litigation.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM:

casebody.head_matter:
684 A.2d 551
COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent, v. Aaron JONES, Petitioner.
Supreme Court of Pennsylvania.
Nov. 12, 1996.
